{"id":110714,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/10/图辑：李光耀夫人柯玉芝/","date":"2010-10-03T17:34:06Z","modified":"2010-10-03T17:34:06Z","title":"图辑：李光耀夫人柯玉芝","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002163350_kwa1_466x350_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"李光耀夫妇和李显龙夫妇\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002163350_kwa1_466x350_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>新加坡前总理李光耀的夫人、现任总理李显龙的母亲柯玉芝女士去世，享年89岁。这是2003年9月为李光耀庆祝80大寿。</p>\n</div></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002163557_kwa2_466x350_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"李光耀、柯玉芝夫妇\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002163557_kwa2_466x350_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>柯玉芝和李光耀1947年在英国留学期间结婚。她被李光耀称为“坚强后盾”。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002163715_kwa3_466x350_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"李光耀、柯玉芝夫妇\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002163715_kwa3_466x350_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>新加坡媒体称柯玉芝是李光耀一生的最爱，两人结婚超过60年鹣鲽情深，夫妻恩爱之深叫许多认识他们的人羡慕不已。</p>\n</div></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002163909_kwa4_466x350_ap.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"李光耀夫妇与印尼总统尤多约诺夫妇\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002163909_kwa4_466x350_ap.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>李光耀、柯玉芝夫妇2006年访问印度尼西亚，受到尤多约诺总统夫妇的欢迎。柯玉芝为人低调，外界对她所知甚少。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002164019_kwa5_466x350_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"李光耀夫妇与英国格洛斯特公爵\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002164019_kwa5_466x350_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>李光耀和柯玉芝共有三个子女，新加坡现任总理李显龙是他们的大儿子。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002164111_kwa6_466x350_afp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"李光耀夫妇\" height=\"80\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x80/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/02/101002164111_kwa6_466x350_afp.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>以优异成绩毕业于英国剑桥大学法律系的柯玉芝多年来是李光耀的贤内助，凡是丈夫出席的场合，必有夫人的身影。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/YZSNCjkmQ1-36E3PaVeY8MlzZPI/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/YZSNCjkmQ1-36E3PaVeY8MlzZPI/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/YZSNCjkmQ1-36E3PaVeY8MlzZPI/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/YZSNCjkmQ1-36E3PaVeY8MlzZPI/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=pdRHJyzM2KQ:Yzm9qL9NCG0:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=pdRHJyzM2KQ:Yzm9qL9NCG0:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=pdRHJyzM2KQ:Yzm9qL9NCG0:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=pdRHJyzM2KQ:Yzm9qL9NCG0:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=pdRHJyzM2KQ:Yzm9qL9NCG0:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=pdRHJyzM2KQ:Yzm9qL9NCG0:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/pdRHJyzM2KQ\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/multimedia/2010/10/101002_pg_mrslee_singapore.shtml\" title=\"图辑：李光耀夫人柯玉芝\">图辑：李光耀夫人柯玉芝</a></p>\n","author":138,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}